{"type":"text","timestamp":1775858013206,"sessionID":"ses_2869e55eeffeo9snU5NGcsmYPh","part":{"id":"prt_d7962d2f3001t8VmqB4wzV6gt1","messageID":"msg_d7962b9e7001Hogzi3TH09Y36D","sessionID":"ses_2869e55eeffeo9snU5NGcsmYPh","type":"text","text":"Now I'll create the tasks.md based on the design and spec documents:","time":{"start":1775858013205,"end":1775858013205}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775858039307,"sessionID":"ses_2869e55eeffeo9snU5NGcsmYPh","part":{"id":"prt_d7962d417001jBEWqyEzWWarZO","messageID":"msg_d7962b9e7001Hogzi3TH09Y36D","sessionID":"ses_2869e55eeffeo9snU5NGcsmYPh","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_f5aefdccbf614a36bbd7cc4b","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-018 — Agentd 空闲清理控制器 Tasks\n\n**Module:** pkg/agentd  \n**Language:** Go  \n**Size:** S  \n**Stage:** ST-3 (Design Complete)\n\n---\n\n## Implementation Tasks\n\n### Phase 1: Package Structure & Constants\n\n- [ ] **T001** Create `pkg/agentd/reconciler.go` with:\n  - Package declaration `package agentd`\n  - Import statements for:\n    - `time`, `context`\n    - `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/api/errors`\n    - `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime`\n    - `k8s.io/klog/v2`\n    - `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox/api/v1alpha1` (sandboxv1alpha1)\n    - `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/client`\n    - `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/controller/controllerutil`\n    - `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/workloadmanager`\n  - Define constant `SessionExpirationTimeout = 15 * time.Minute`\n  - Define constant `lastActivityAnnotationKey = \"last-activity-time\"` (local reference to workloadmanager constant)\n\n### Phase 2: Reconciler Implementation\n\n- [ ] **T010** Implement `Reconciler` struct in `pkg/agentd/reconciler.go`:\n  ```go\n  type Reconciler struct {\n      client.Client\n      Scheme *runtime.Scheme\n  }\n  ```\n\n- [ ] **T011** Implement `Reconcile` method with exact algorithm:\n  1. Get Sandbox object by namespaced name\n  2. If NotFound, return empty result\n  3. If other error, return error\n  4. Read `last-activity-time` annotation\n  5. If annotation exists and non-empty:\n     - Parse RFC3339 timestamp\n     - If parse error, return RequeueAfter: 30s with error\n     - Compute expirationTime = lastActivity.Add(SessionExpirationTimeout)\n     - If now After expirationTime: delete Sandbox, ignore NotFound errors\n     - Else: return RequeueAfter: time.Until(expirationTime)\n  6. Return empty result\n\n- [ ] **T012** Implement `SetupWithManager` function:\n  ```go\n  func (r *Reconciler) SetupWithManager(mgr ctrl.Manager) error {\n      return ctrl.NewControllerManagedBy(mgr).\n          For(&sandboxv1alpha1.Sandbox{}).\n          Complete(r)\n  }\n  ```\n\n- [ ] **T013** Add necessary controller-runtime imports (`sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime`)\n\n### Phase 3: Binary Entry Point\n\n- [ ] **T020** Create `cmd/agentd/main.go` with:\n  - Package main\n  - Import statements:\n    - `runtime` (k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime)\n    - `utilruntime` (k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/util/runtime)\n    - `ctrl \"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime\"`\n    - `metricsserver \"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/metrics/server\"`\n    - Core Kubernetes types via k8s.io/api (for scheme)\n    - sandboxv1alpha1 (for scheme)\n    - `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/agentd`\n  - init() function to register schemes:\n    ```go\n    var schemeBuilder = runtime.NewScheme()\n\n    func init() {\n        utilruntime.Must(scheme.AddToScheme(schemeBuilder))\n        utilruntime.Must(sandboxv1alpha1.AddToScheme(schemeBuilder))\n    }\n    ```\n  - Main function with manager setup:\n    ```go\n    mgr, err := ctrl.NewManager(ctrl.GetConfigOrDie(), ctrl.Options{\n        Scheme:                 schemeBuilder,\n        Metrics:                metricsserver.Options{BindAddress: \"0\"},\n        HealthProbeBindAddress: \"0\",\n    })\n    ```\n  - Register controller:\n    ```go\n    err = ctrl.NewControllerManagedBy(mgr).\n        For(&sandboxv1alpha1.Sandbox{}).\n        Complete(&agentd.Reconciler{\n            Client: mgr.GetClient(),\n            Scheme: mgr.GetScheme(),\n        })\n    ```\n  - Start manager: `mgr.Start(ctrl.SetupSignalHandler())`\n\n### Phase 4: Unit Tests\n\n- [ ] **T030** Create `pkg/agentd/reconciler_test.go`:\n  - Test Reconcile returns nil when Sandbox not found\n  - Test Reconcile skips deletion when no annotation\n  - Test Reconcile deletes when expired (last-activity-time > 15 min ago)\n  - Test Reconcile requeues with correct duration when not expired\n  - Test Reconcile requeues 30s on parse error\n  - Test Reconcile handles NotFound on delete gracefully\n\n- [ ] **T031** Add table-driven tests for time parsing edge cases\n\n### Phase 5: Build & Verify\n\n- [ ] **T040** Run `go mod tidy` - ensure dependencies resolved\n\n- [ ] **T041** Run `go build ./cmd/agentd` - verify build succeeds\n\n- [ ] **T042** Run `go test ./pkg/agentd/...` - verify all unit tests pass\n\n- [ ] **T043** Run `go vet ./pkg/agentd/...` - verify no vet errors\n\n---\n\n## Dependencies\n\n- **T001**: None (new package)\n- **T010**: T001\n- **T011**: T010\n- **T012**: T010\n- **T013**: T010\n- **T020**: T012 (requires reconciler import)\n- **T030**: T011 (tests Reconcile method)\n- **T031**: T030\n- **T040**: All implementation tasks\n- **T041**: T020\n- **T042**: T030, T031\n- **T043**: T041\n\n---\n\n## Configuration Variables\n\n| Variable | Required | Default | Description |\n|----------|----------|---------|-------------|\n| None | - | - | No runtime configuration required - uses fixed 15 minute timeout |\n\n---\n\n## Architecture Notes\n\n### Data Structures\n\n```go\n// pkg/agentd/reconciler.go\nconst SessionExpirationTimeout = 15 * time.Minute\nconst lastActivityAnnotationKey = \"last-activity-time\"\n\ntype Reconciler struct {\n    client.Client\n    *runtime.Scheme\n}\n```\n\n### Constants\n\n| Constant | Value | Description |\n|----------|-------|-------------|\n| SessionExpirationTimeout | 15 * time.Minute | Idle session expiration threshold |\n| lastActivityAnnotationKey | \"last-activity-time\" | Annotation key for last activity timestamp |\n\n### Key Behaviors\n\n1. **Reconcile flow**:\n   - Get Sandbox → NotFound? → return nil\n   - Read `last-activity-time` annotation → missing/empty? → return nil\n   - Parse timestamp → error? → return RequeueAfter(30s) with error\n   - Compute expiration → expired? → Delete, ignore NotFound\n   - Not expired → return RequeueAfter(time.Until(expirationTime))\n\n2. **Idempotency**: Delete NotFound = success\n\n3. **Manager config**: Metrics disabled, health probe disabled\n\n---\n\n## References\n\n- Design Doc: `idle-cleanup/design.md`\n- Spec Doc: `idle-cleanup/spec.md`\n- Delta Spec: `changes/AR-018/delta-spec.md`\n- Workload Manager (annotation key): `pkg/workloadmanager/gc.go:666`\n- Sandbox API: `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox/api/v1alpha1`","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-018/tasks.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/pkg/store/store_valkey.go\">\nERROR [157:44] vs.cli.B().Zadd().Key(vs.expiryIndexKey).ZaddScoreMember undefined (type cmds.ZaddKey has no field or method ZaddScoreMember)\nERROR [157:67] undefined: valkey.ZaddScoreMember\nERROR [158:50] vs.cli.B().Zadd().Key(vs.lastActivityIndexKey).ZaddScoreMember undefined (type cmds.ZaddKey has no field or method ZaddScoreMember)\nERROR [158:73] undefined: valkey.ZaddScoreMember\nERROR [338:65] vs.cli.B().Zadd().Key(vs.lastActivityIndexKey).Score undefined (type cmds.ZaddKey has no field or method Score)\nERROR [348:9] vs.cli.Close() (no value) used as value\n</diagnostics>\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/cmd/picod/main.go\">\nERROR [24:39] not enough arguments in call to picod.NewServer\n\thave (*picod.Config)\n\twant (*picod.Config, *picod.AuthConfig)\n</diagnostics>\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/pkg/router/jwt.go\">\nERROR [4:2] \"cryp